<title>ITALY: Euromobiliare decides on share swap ratio.</title>
<headline>Euromobiliare decides on share swap ratio.</headline>
<dateline>MILAN 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Italian investment house Euromobiliare and Credito Emiliano bank (Credem) said on Thursday that they had agreed a share swap ratio for their planned merger.</p>
<p>A joint statement from the two financial groups said that Mediobanca had indicated a share swap ratio of 13 Euromobiliare ordinary shares for each ordinary share of Credem. This proposal will be put to extraordinary meetings of the two groups during the summer.</p>
<p>-- Milan newsroom +392 66129502</p>
